"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-19-fans-loving-mongolias-olympics-opening-ceremony-uniforms-21253478\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"TheOlympicsis about watching the world's best athletes battle it out for gold medals, but it's also about pomp and circumstance.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony especially is an extravagant affair, offering countries a chance to show off their top stars in national dress-inspired looks while they proudly waving their flags.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, though, one country in particular is catching everyone's eyes.\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mongolia's Olympic opening ceremony uniform is winning praise all over the internet for its 'majestic' feel.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so beloved, in fact, that some have even said Mongolia has 'won the Olympics before it's even begun'.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the opening ceremony for the Paris Olympics 2024 is yet to take place,countries are already showing off their ensembles for the on July 26 event online.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Mongolia, among a few others, has seriously impressed people.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the East Asian nation's uniforms, designed by Mongolian couture brand,\\u00a0Michel & Amazonka, were unveiled on Instagram this week, they were described as looking like something off a runway.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9784388521737836, \"rank\": 0.022029968921473003, \"text\": \"East Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Asia\"}, {\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7293293301380301, \"rank\": 0.3700761548062629, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.576744690108081e-30, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Really stunning combination of Mongolian and Hellenistic influences,' wrote @Janefrome in the comments.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7293293301380301, \"rank\": 0.3700761548062629, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenistic_period\", \"score\": 0.7713471128379964, \"rank\": 0.2964230913166721, \"text\": \"Hellenistic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenistic_period\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellenistic_period\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Divine.'\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another, @annfosnacht22, said: 'All of their clothes are so elegant.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Such beautiful detailing', while @reinerenier wrote: 'This is better than LV, Dior, etc, congratulations, this is a masterpiece'.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mongolia won Best Dressed for sure | short video  The love did not stop there either.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Twitter, @Giggabseddad wrote: 'This is what loving your heritage, culture, and history looks like.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0748989772191199e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amazing job Mongolia!'\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One user, @MugsM, also shed some light on the uniform's historical influences, explaining: 'It's designed by sister duo Michel and Amazonka and said to be inspired by the Mongolian national costume called deel'.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 0.9999999831347851, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7293293301380301, \"rank\": 0.3700761548062629, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deel is a traditional piece of clothing worn by Turkic, Tungusic, and Mongolian peoples for centuries.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkic_peoples\", \"score\": 0.9999561036150694, \"rank\": 4.388451885176799e-05, \"text\": \"Turkic\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkic_peoples\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkic_peoples\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tungusic_peoples\", \"score\": 0.996019208376063, \"rank\": 0.0039967016606259065, \"text\": \"Tungusic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tungusic_peoples\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tungusic_peoples\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mongolian peoples\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be made from materials like silk, wool, or cotton.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Mongolia, the deel symbolises equality and the human body's smoothness and straightness.\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In aFacebook post, designers Michel and Amazonka, who are sisters, explained the meticulous process that helped them design the outfits.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 0.9999999831347851, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We took the detailed measurements of each athlete's body and made them individually in our workshop with the labor of 42 Mongolians for more than 3 months,' she said.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.5716741980453941, \"rank\": 0.7492408689619089, \"text\": \"Mongolians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In doing so, it is an elaborate work that took an average of 20 hours to make just one set in six stages.'\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Replying to @Estefan\\u00eda#mongolia#olympics#paris2024  Alongside Mongolia, others have managed to steal the show ahead of it even happening, Haiti being one of them.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"score\": 0.9999945266735897, \"rank\": 4.506663717718811e-06, \"text\": \"Haiti\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Haiti's uniform was designed by Italian-Haitian designer Stella Jean, and incorporated the country's cultural heritage.\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2676, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their look is made from traditional materials, with vibrant colours blending African and indigenous influences, including prints painted by a Haitian artist.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\", \"score\": 0.999292181879601, \"rank\": 0.0006621882030793662, \"text\": \"Haitian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haitian_Vodou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twitter user @Leneslife said: 'Haiti and Mongolia's Olympic 2024 uniforms??\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They won my heart.\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The designers went tf in.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The respective cultures are expressed so beautifully.\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stella Jean and Michel and Amazonka?\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3074, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 0.9999999831347851, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You all did that.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you.'\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Haiti Olympic Ceremony Outfits Explained!\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ad\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b9Haitian-Italian designer Stella Jean, a pioneer in promoting diversity & inclusivity in the fashion industry, is set to design uniforms for Team Haiti at the Paris Olympics.Source: erikabazholland/TikTokpic.twitter.com/53pPdo9X5j  Certain countries, however, are not receiving the same positive praise.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US, for example, which saw its team decked out in Ralph Lauren, failed to win fans.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3503, \"end\": 3505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9988952152718332, \"rank\": 0.0006135793068288768, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3553, \"end\": 3565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9981537128581838, \"rank\": 0.0018497022231027667, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@YabiKeikai wrote: 'Team Mongolia looks like royalty of a galactic empire.\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3613, \"end\": 3621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA looks like the pool staff at a cheap resort hotel.'\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3663, \"end\": 3671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8000706947182916, \"rank\": 0.24983656496751724, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same sentiment was shared for the UK's Olympic look, with @Zombiedawgs commenting: 'Mongolia has the hardest f***ing fit in Olympic history and TeamGB's outfit looks like a f***ing ASOS advert.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3763, \"end\": 3765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999940804816687, \"rank\": 3.2831321910153698e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3813, \"end\": 3821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960032255, \"rank\": 3.995125034079697e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 3910, \"end\": 3914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Automated_airport_weather_station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3066716713923804e-15, \"text\": \"ASOS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Automated_airport_weather_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Automated_airport_weather_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Embarrassing.'\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tough crowd.\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a story to share?\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch by emailingMetroLifestyleTeam@Metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic team captain sent home for smoking cigarettes and drinking alcohol  ArrowMORE:Team GB gold medal hope Josh Kerr has message for rival ahead of Paris  ArrowMORE:Olympian amputates his broken finger to compete at Paris 2024\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4202, \"end\": 4207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.028815014832861e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4219, \"end\": 4227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999843921615, \"rank\": 1.4937559280413966e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 4270, \"end\": 4280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998772182, \"rank\": 1.2261403524716877e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}]}"